text: Candice Susan Swanepoel is a South African model. ==Career== In 2010, Swanepoel became a Victoria's Secret Angel. In 2013, she wore the "Royal Fantasy Bra", a multi-million dollar bra, during their annual fashion show. ==References== Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:Afrikaner people Category:South African models
